423
00:16:08,519 --> 00:16:10,260
He just screwed himself.

424
00:16:10,303 --> 00:16:11,217
Let's go.

425
00:16:11,261 --> 00:16:12,697
Walk away.

426
00:16:12,740 --> 00:16:15,178
Until we meet again, Counselor.

