00:16:36,069 --> 00:16:37,766
He lived down the street.

435
00:16:37,810 --> 00:16:39,594
I was 14 when he was murdered.

436
00:16:39,638 --> 00:16:41,857
According to the case file,
Frank's murder

437
00:16:41,901 --> 00:16:44,860
